{"tid":691562,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"賤種朗征世盃前 賀無老母的龍鳳胎1歲生日","createTime":"2018-06-06T00:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T02:55:34.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"877970d5884e3d1f822075165ac462f056675a98","tid":691562,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T00:57:36.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=CnfZj3ErIPuV8b4ntSdHazA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=320f3599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】世界盃前夕，葡萄牙球星基斯坦奴朗拿度迎來一絲平靜，周二和龍鳳胎首次慶祝生日。<br />\n皇家馬德里射手基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）於instagram上載相片，與女友洛迪古絲、兒子小C朗、一對龍鳳胎Eva和Mateo、年紀最小的Alana Martina於泳池上的合照，C朗更在這家庭照上說：「我的兒女Eva和Mateo今天正慶祝他們第一個生日。恭喜，我親愛的孩子！」<span style=\"color: red;\">有傳這兩名孩子都是由代母所生。</span><br />\n<br />\nEva和Mateo這對龍鳳胎出生於距離墨西哥邊境僅20英里的加州小鎮La Mesa，據當地報章報道，Eva於早上9時07分先出生，數分鐘後Mateo便出世，兩人的生日都在今屆俄羅斯世界盃舉行前，其父親C朗將會帶領葡萄牙繼2016年於歐國盃奪冠後，於世界盃再創佳績。"},{"pid":"09b1aa594ad62aae28c7ed395f5382d67606d9b0","tid":691562,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3ef1ac99b45aa1b25207aa4f0f3763f01ce3d9","tid":691562,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:06:17.000Z","msg":"9點鐘王sir 仲準時過4點鐘許sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48b5228ae3f7fee48ff654a1fd85c45428e144b","tid":691562,"uid":186784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"咁快1年了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}